author: Just Jared
title: Beyonce's Baby Bump Breaks Instagram Record For Likes
text:
Beyonce is breaking records.
The 35-year-old entertainer’s baby announcement, featuring a photo of her baby bump , officially has the most likes on Instagram now, according to Variety .
PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Beyonce 
The photo received 6.33 million likes in only 8 hours and has over 333,000 comments.
The previous record-holder was a picture of Selena Gomez sipping a Coke from June 2016, which garnered 6.3 million likes to-date.
Bey boasts a whopping 92.8 million followers on the social media app.
The only celebs ahead of her are Selena (108.4 million), Taylor Swift (96.8 million), and Ariana Grande (95.4 million).
A photo posted by Beyoncé (@beyonce) on Feb 1, 2017 at 10:39am PST
